OL,3,CWoman slams corridor care after two
OL,4,Cdays on hospital floor after heart
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA woman has spoken out about her
OL,8,Fexperience of waiting two days in a
OL,9,Fhospital corridor after her heart
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FIt comes as the Senedd debated a
OL,13,Fpetition which has reached over 10,000
OL,14,Fsignatures calling for the end of
OL,15,Fcorridor care.
