OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe petition was jointly written by
OL,8,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN) and
OL,9,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,10,Fafter their members across Wales
OL,11,Freported serious concerns about the
OL,12,Fharm corridor care was causing
OL,13,Fpatients and staff.
OL,15,FProtesters gathered outside the Senedd
OL,16,Fon Wednesday afternoon demanding
OL,17,Furgent action be taken to end the
OL,18,Fpractice.
