OL,7,FIn the petition the RCN and BMA urged
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government to begin
OL,9,Frecording corridor care cases in Wales
OL,10,Fand pledge to make it a 'never event'
OL,11,Ffor patients to receive care in chairs
OL,12,Ffor more than 24 hours.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government says care in
OL,15,Fundesignated or non-clinical
OL,16,Fenvironments is 'not acceptable' and
OL,17,Fsays it's 'determined to eliminate
OL,18,Fthis practice through system-wide
OL,19,Freform'
