OL,3,CWoman slams corridor care after two
OL,4,Cdays on hospital floor after heart
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIn March Liz Elford arrived at the
OL,8,FRoyal Glamorgan Hospital after feeling
OL,9,Funwell at work.
OL,11,FShe was quickly seen in A&E and told
OL,12,Fshe had suffered a heart attack that
OL,13,Fmorning.
OL,15,FAfter this, Liz said she was moved to
OL,16,Fa chair on a corridor where she stayed
OL,17,Ffor the next two days.
