OL,3,CWoman slams corridor care after two
OL,4,Cdays on hospital floor after heart
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"When you're sat there feeling very
OL,8,Fvulnerable, the last place you want to
OL,9,Fbe is virtually on show in a corridor
OL,10,Fjust looking at a brick wall. To be
OL,11,Fquite honest it didn't do any good for
OL,12,Fmy mental health" she said.
OL,14,F"For the two nights I actually slept
OL,15,Fon the floor in the corridor" Liz
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FDespite Liz' experience she praised
OL,19,Fthe staff who she described as
OL,20,F"superb".
