OL,7,FLiz said it was only after a nurse who
OL,8,Fwas on duty when she originally came
OL,9,Fin recognised her, was she then moved
OL,10,Fto a more suitable place in the
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,FLiz added that if "If they do have to
OL,14,Fuse these corridors , make it a bit
OL,15,Fmore private".
OL,17,FCwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,18,FBoard, which runs the Royal Glamorgan
OL,19,FHospital, said:
