OL,7,F"We recognise that there are occasions
OL,8,Fwhere care has been delivered in less
OL,9,Fthan optimal environments for our
OL,10,Fpatients, but as a Health Board, we do
OL,11,Fnot administer corridor care.
OL,13,F"We are unable to comment on
OL,14,Findividual cases, therefore we would
OL,15,Fencourage the patient to contact our
OL,16,FConcerns Team so we can listen to
OL,17,Ftheir concerns and address them
OL,18,Fthrough our formal process."
