OL,7,FThe Welsh NHS confederation which
OL,8,Frepresents the NHS local health boards
OL,9,Fand trusts in Wales said treating
OL,10,Fpatients in corridors is "unsuitable,
OL,11,Fundignified and potentially unsafe."
OL,13,FHowever, the NHS confederation argues
OL,14,Fcorridor care is a "symptom of wider
OL,15,Fsystem pressures" including the
OL,16,F"fragility in the social care sector."
