OL,7,FThey added "banning corridor care
OL,8,Fwithout tackling underlying issues
OL,9,Frisks worsening ambulance delays and
OL,10,Fharming patients elsewhere in the
OL,11,Fsystem."
OL,13,FIn the debate the Health Secretary
OL,14,FJeremy Miles MS rejected the petitions
OL,15,Fcalls to categorise corridor care as a
OL,16,F'never event', but affirmed his
OL,17,Fcommitment to try and end the practice.
OL,19,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said
OL,20,Fin a statement:
