OL,7,F"Care in undesignated or non-clinical
OL,8,Fenvironments is not acceptable. It
OL,9,Fcompromises patient dignity, safety,
OL,10,Fand staff wellbeing.
OL,12,F"We have provided in excess of #200m
OL,13,Fadditional funding this year to help
OL,14,Fpeople leave hospital when they are
OL,15,Fready ensuring they receive the right
OL,16,Fcare, in the right place and at the
OL,17,Fright time.
